snippet: Russell Henley became the first PGA Tour rookie to win his debut in 10 years with a record-setting performance in the Sony Open in Honolulu.
abstract: PGA Tour rookie Russell Henley wins Sony Open tennis tournament in Honolulu, giving him an invitation into the Masters.
lead_paragraph: Russell Henley became the first PGA Tour rookie to win his debut in 10 years with a record-setting performance in the Sony Open in Honolulu.

headline.seo: Rookie Russell Henley Wins Sony Open
headline.main: PGA Tour Rookie Wins Sony Open
